Premier ministre ya Grande bretagne Boris Johnson mpe president ya Batswana bazwi coronavirus ya sika COVID-19. Bokono bwango bokoti ti epayi ya bakambi ya Commission ya Union africaine. Bamitieyi na na kobombama. 
 "Banda 24 heures, namitie na bokangami mpo nzoto na nga emoisi billembo ya mike mike mpe nasalaki test, ebimi positif na coromavirus. Namikangi na ndako kasi nakokoba kokamba mbulamatari ntango tozali kobundisa virus oyo," elobi na vidéo na Twitter M. Johnson. 
Mokambi ya Commission ya Union africaine Moussa Faki Mahamat ye mpe amikangi na ndaku mpo azalaki nzinganzinga ya mosungi na ye moko azwami na COVID-19. 
Moto yango azali moyi ïle Maurice, azali na mibu 72 mpe wautaki na RDC o’mokolo mwa le 14 mars. 
Président ya Botswana mpe azwa yango. Akoti ndaku, ye mpe lokola.